<section class="index-section section">
  <div class="index-container container">
    <h2 class="title is-2 deep-lavender has-text-centered section-title">Fueling adoption in the EU<br>
      blockchain ecosystem</h2>

    <div class="rock-icons columns">
        <div id="index-column-technology-rock" class="rock-icon column left-side">
          <div class="rock-icon container left-side">
            <img class="small-rock-2" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
            <img class="small-rock-1" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
            <img src="/assets/rock-technology.png" srcset="/assets/rock-technology@2x.png 2x, assets/rock-technology@3x.png 3x" class="rock-technology">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="index-column-technology-text" class="rock-icon-text column right-side">
          <div class="text-rock-icon right-side">
            <h3 class="title dark-indigo subsection-title">Technology</h3>
            <p class="index-information-text steel">LTO Network is the easiest blockchain to integrate. The node modifies to your existing (legacy) systems instead of changing your software to be compatible with blockchain technology.</p>
            <a class="read-more-link "href="#" >
              <p class="read-more deep-lavender"><br>Read more →</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="community rock-icons columns">

      <div id="index-column-community-text" class="rock-icon-text column left-side">
        <div class="text-rock-icon left-side">
          <h3 class="title dark-indigo subsection-title">Community</h3>
          <p class="index-information-text steel">LTO Network is known for its amazing community. Learn more about the distributed workforce to see how you can help with your talents.</p>
          <a class="read-more-link "href="#" >
            <p class="read-more deep-lavender"><br>Read more →</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="index-column-community-rock" class="column rock-icon right-side">
        <div class="rock-icon container right-side">
          <img src="/assets/rock-community.png" srcset="/assets/rock-community@2x.png 2x, /assets/rock-community@3x.png 3x" class="rock-community">

          <img class="small-rock-3" src="/assets/small-rock-3.svg">
          <img class="small-rock-4" src="/assets/small-rock-4.svg">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="rock-icons columns">

        <div id="index-column-ecosystem-rock" class="rock-icon column left-side">
          <div class="rock-icon container left-side">
            <img class="small-rock-5" src="/assets/small-rock-5.svg">

            <img src="/assets/rock-ecossystem.png" srcset="/assets/rock-ecossystem@2x.png 2x, /assets/rock-ecossystem@3x.png 3x" class="rock-ecossystem">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="index-column-ecosystem-text" class="rock-icon-text column right-side">
          <div class="text-rock-icon right-side">
            <h3 class="title dark-indigo subsection-title">Ecosystem</h3>
            <p class="index-information-text steel">Blockchain has been around for 10 years, without significant adoption. LTO Network breaks with this narrative through our ecosystem V.</p>
            <a class="read-more-link "href="#" >
              <p class="read-more deep-lavender"><br>Read more → </p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

